    "longBusinessSummary": "Fortune Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank provides banking products and services in Vietnam. The company offers current and dual accounts; savings account; and loans, including short-term loans for production and business or installment, home, project housing, home construction and renovation, car, unsecured and secured consumer, agricultural and rural development, investment and development of macadamia trees, and retirement credit loans. It also provides life and non-life insurance products; credit, debit, and prepaid cards; domestic payment services; international money transfer and remittance services; foreign exchange services; and other services. In addition, the company offers corporate products comprising deposit products; loans, such as short-term credit line, financial support commitment, refinancing, credit for construction contractors, macadamia seedlings, and macadamia nut purchasing and processing loans; trade finance services; international and domestic guarantee services; and digital retail banking services. Fortune Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank was formerly known as Lien Viet Post Joint Stock Commercial Bank and changed its name to Fortune Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank in July 2024. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
